    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your<strong> cannellini beans</strong></p><p>Once the shallot has slightly softened, add the<strong> drained cannellini beans </strong>and <strong>chopped green beans </strong>to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until the beans have begun to soften</p>",
